{"tid":1386303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發! 電子傳媒從業員給香港人的信[轉發]","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T12:09:08.000Z","uid":201531,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1d49bce78bda3a18f16585e2e4ee5c59145492f6","tid":1386303,"uid":201531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:07:39.000Z","msg":"致香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群電子傳媒從業員。我們的日常工作，就是提供資訊娛樂予廣大觀眾，因此深深明白掌握群眾脈搏的重要，構思一旦脫離觀市民期望，所製作的節目就會遭到唾棄，因此，林鄭政府今日所面對的困局，我們非常了解。<br />\n<br />\n由今年年初開始，林鄭政府正在編寫一齣連續劇，劇本由一宗台灣殺人案作序幕，引發香港市民反送中惡法，場面波瀾壯闊，吸引全世界追看，當時若果林鄭以全面撤回惡法作結，不失為一部大團圓結局的劇本。可惜，編劇者完全無視市民意願，卻反其道而行，發展成無數次的警民衝突，警察以形同謀殺的手段對付示威者、途人、記者、社工，血腥暴力的情節，早已超越電檢尺度。更甚者，編劇者竟加入古惑仔橋段，警黑互通，橫行無忌，令市民心痛惡絕。<br />\n<br />\n事到如今，林鄭政府所撰寫的劇本已經完全爛透，更犧牲了市民的血淚和性命作代價，百年福地，變作危城。我們認為要挽救香港，政府別無選擇，必須立即回應港人五大訴求（撤回逃犯條例修訂、撤回612暴動定義、不追究抗爭者、獨立徹查警暴，與及全面落實雙普選）。與此同時，警隊亦必須徹底改革，重建1997年前的文明精銳，讓電視劇中警隊的正義英勇故事不至淪為瘋狂攪笑節目。<br />\n<br />\n作為面向全港市民的電子傳媒從業員，我們定必繼續堅守崗位以服務大眾。同時，我們的角色也是香港人，視香港為家為根，我們會密切留意這齣連續劇的發展，並跟所有理念相同的香港人團結一致，一同以自己雙手改寫結局！<br />\n<br />\n香港加油！<br />\n<br />\n一群熱愛香港的電子傳媒從業員上<br />\n2019年7月30日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cp1yewQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcp1yewQ.png&h=5208eedd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4YXEUwR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4YXEUwR.png&h=55d2c404&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gHBN3qc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgHBN3qc.png&h=44a3899a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EqUDqDx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqUDqDx.png&h=ad52f1a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3zv1bT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3zv1bT.png&h=87a254f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZxQ1bU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZxQ1bU.png&h=30f7dd13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/criHSiA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcriHSiA.png&h=9c93b90f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUys3qf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiUys3qf.png&h=b2b680cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Ja3BLg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Ja3BLg.png&h=1b522669&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f81ede825ae587011d7324b388dab52c62e46fa5","tid":1386303,"uid":201531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172f9323cee5b6296a75d98a36029721f2e5d698","tid":1386303,"uid":201531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"60e5abe4eb311f9560219ebfbef07e79043f34d1","tid":1386303,"uid":201531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c97d1ecc6d6b54782aabcab373657e350748e0a","tid":1386303,"uid":201531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:10:17.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"ca56c64a6f71725e55b61ed6f6e3f9a33592a95f","tid":1386303,"uid":201531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710c59140792ead7411fe5e583b238dcc80b19bb","tid":1386303,"uid":201531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f5179675aa66d632bd375b15a915d6295c21c350","tid":1386303,"uid":201531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899e20ac007002b3423dc3b3a602a7a3c865371e","tid":1386303,"uid":201531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,